    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Instruments for measuring the external dimensions of the skulls of deceased beings; for devices to measure the skulls of living beings, use "cephalometers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
